a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/111%2c%e6%98%93%2c201%2c20220525%2c2/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,111,易,201,20220525,2","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"易","JNO":"201","JDATE":"20220525","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}